trans-unit.source: Describes the original settings of the <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TYPEFLAGS"></xref> in the COM type library from which the type was imported.
trans-unit.target: Beskriver opprinnelige innstillingene for den <xref href="System.Runtime.InteropServices.TYPEFLAGS"> </xref> i COM typebiblioteket typen ble importert fra.

trans-unit.source: `TypeLibTypeFlags` is used along with the <xref:System.Runtime.InteropServices.TypeLibTypeAttribute>.
The flags are retained for reference only.
They are not used by the common language runtime.
trans-unit.target: De brukes ikke av common language runtime.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see `TYPEFLAGS` in the MSDN library.
trans-unit.target: Hvis du vil ha mer informasjon, se `TYPEFLAGS` i MSDN-biblioteket.
